# Component Rules

Every UI element must be a reusable component. Do NOT duplicate.

Required shared components in `src/components/shared/`:
Button, Dropdown, Modal, SearchBar, Sidebar, CardTile, CollectionRow, PriceBadge, MarketBadge, Pagination, Checkbox, Tabs, Tooltip, ContextMenu, DataTable, BulkActionBar, EmptyState, PageHeader, CardDetailSheet

Feature pages compose shared components — no inline one-off UI.
